  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>もう！
カイウスがちゃんとしないから
変なケンカ売られるんじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Honestly! It's 'cause you can't
do things the right way that you
keep getting into weird fights.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いやいや。
ケンカ売ってるのはいつも
ルビアの方じゃないのかよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Uh, no, no.
Pretty sure it's always you picking fights.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウスがもっとちゃんとしてれば
あたしだって怒ったりしないわよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If you actually did things the right way,
I wouldn't have to get angry!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちゃんとって……どうしろってんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The right way... What are you even talking about?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
